t differ between treatments, indicating that the two groups used similar amounts of energy. Our results suggest that behavioural flexibility allows hibernating E. fuscus to maintain water balance and reduce energy costs across a wide range of hibernation humidities.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Muise, Kristina A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Dzal, Yvonne A.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Fletcher, Quinn E.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Willis, Craig K. R.", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/4328cadb0eef90a419296466c5177cbd", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/f3c16a8b48b4b04b8f595fcfda3ef18fbabaaf636c8c5ee9aec35d62ebc11664", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/MARL4YY4", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/MARL4YY4", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/2ad6ff58c4c012635916fd0f842d4529!/b114257-116709", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/ce1e7618f237ff56e74d51f496e811a3", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "5", "pages": "jeb246699", "title": "Journal of Experimental Biology", "volume": "227"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/4328cadb0eef90a419296466c5177cbd"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:MARL4YY4"}, {"identifier": "10.1242/jeb.2466